    <h1>Assistants</h1><div class="paragraph">
<p>When logging in to your system for the first time you are greeted by our virtual helpers: the assistants. You can find them under <strong>Setup</strong>.<br>
Finally a quick and simple way of setting up your system without having to understand complex contexts? Yes! Our assistants will help you setting up your system step by step without any instructions or prior knowledge.<br>
Just give it a go!<br>
In the following section you will find an overview of all currently available assistants and their functions.</p>
